text: The Big Freeze is the fifth studio album by Laura Stevenson, The album was released by Don Giovanni Records on March 29, 2019. It debuted on the Billboard charts at #11 Alternative New Artist Albums, #35 for Heatseekers Albums, and #41 for Current Alternative Albums. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:Laura Stevenson albums Category:2019 albums Category:Don Giovanni Records albums
